ch.hevs.cloudio.endpoint

Class CloudioAdLibNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.hevs.cloudio.endpoint.CloudioNode
      • ch.hevs.cloudio.endpoint.CloudioAdLibNode

  • public class CloudioAdLibNode
extends CloudioNode
    The CloudioAdLibNode class allows you to create the structure of a cloud.iO node at runtime in contrast to the static model used by the CloudioNode class. TODO: Example.

      • declareImplementedInterface

        public void declareImplementedInterface(java.lang.String interface_)
